{"tid":2354941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：特朗普據報擬前往蘇格蘭打高球　蘇格蘭稱屬非必要旅遊","createTime":"2021-01-06T00:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T00:31:16.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3010187b17763c98223c00e7c706cde0137774","tid":2354941,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:28:25.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普據報打算前往英國蘇格蘭打高爾夫球，<strong>以避過出席今個月20日舉行的總統就職典禮。</strong><br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭首席部長施雅晴說，不清楚特朗普的計劃，<strong>但因應疫情大流行，目前只容許必要的旅遊，有關規定亦適用於特朗普，認為打高爾夫球不是必要目的。</strong><br />\n<br />\n特朗普在蘇格蘭艾爾郡和阿伯丁郡，都擁有高爾夫球場，白宮至今未公布特朗普當日的行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568845-20210106.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568845-20210106.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=085b75de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568845-20210106.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=53b0b5b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568845-20210106.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"449d8edeb58ce4299b74f88e198070dbb4221158","tid":2354941,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"仲有心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302bab4cd95aa292a2e3f0568dc9d13e403840b9","tid":2354941,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}